Package jrtr.swrenderer

An renderer based on software rasterization implementing the jrtr interfaces.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SWJPanel
    Shows the bitmap rendered by the the software renderer.
    SWRenderContext
    A skeleton for a software renderer.
    SWRenderPanel
    Implements a panel for a software renderer.
    SWShader
    Manages shaders for the software renderer.
    SWTexture
    Manages textures for the software renderer.
    SWVertexData
    A simple implementation of VertexData which does not add any additional functionality.

Package jrtr.swrenderer Description

An renderer based on software rasterization implementing the jrtr interfaces. Implementation of the rasterizer is subject of a programming assignment.
